      "content": "i dont think i can do another night of this. the nerve pain is just... it's constant. there's no break. no sleep. just this burning that never stops. i'm so tired of fighting just to exist in a body that feels like it's constantly attacking me. i just want everything to be quiet. i just want the stillness.",
