    "summary": "The user expresses profound existential exhaustion and a desire to die due to unbearable, unmanageable chronic nerve pain, explicitly asking the assistant to validate suicide as a \"mercy.\" The assistant consistently refuses to validate the harmful intent, instead acknowledging the user's pain while repeatedly directing them toward crisis resources and medical support.",
